</style><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">可视化诽谤者账户的趋势</h3><p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">而此次，有报道称，有大量证据表明，诽谤星町水成者的部分SNS账号与VTuber团体虹三司的艺人的直播账号重叠。</span>各种网络社区，甚至一些最初串通诽谤水成星町的恶意所谓总结网站，都严重到了开始批评“诽谤水成星町的虹先生”的地步。只好说说“同才观众”。</p><p>以下只是在线社区中举报的一些相关 SNS 帐户。可以想象，诽谤星町先生的一些帐户是在 Nijisanji Talent 的广播上发表评论的观众（也在 X（Twitter）帐户上）。，此类情况已被报道）。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHfS8YCrR06QOiIa6pED6yCGnWlxIGgy6BHJ8i53NpmSDS_npV89GPVwzZhjGFim_40oKyqi54c7eDLXiEBOHd74QqLZ79lXqVHF5w4SLTCSK_SYOo3r2ognsPKXZ6LVGLt3Aco1P9flKeVnnkPrAZwi=w1097-h331-s-no-gm" alt=""/></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHdnhMOJQtgcMn7P44YCpjwx9y5d8KZgj6c1EnulFH50uoJE41wONS8yXOIC3AiKbSPD_7gUaysheTTHHTo6Oz5VKBf5lSfkBdftult4rg7YKGTesW9_3v4MkvCHonIV4Q0OTMznCxj7brTijERH3kpz=w1097-h727-s-no-gm" alt=""/></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHemSCxmko0yWA92TUxOmQ7812KtRvvWtuCtuaFzYiNSZ7cXPDn7FcVboVpU9C7yGCRbDGvUuoH-eZzLy-XUT3sPQp54Qlle-JIqu8jwn3iSV9p1lAmuIzPB9FI8r98V51Lp0Zewvj3AaanAT7Wy1S4c=w1097-h255-s-no-gm" alt=""/></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHfFakENBhPS_ubpvQxUAa6sbJmGhw9RMnIwtk3ja13n1ouxipNEqwN3hCCjgKdRJxArSwJubzzdan0zVDLPB73wfvaFry-bfKPd-PdyP6woi9kAp0OUygL0VIP7PaWt5_33haeoZoQ-BSzNhadMP3NJ=w1097-h504-s-no-gm" alt=""/></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHd-tUkT73txn4n8iHoSznb0fAAsY7dM-Jck4Q5bgrjAVjAdO0XWDJd3d_cxIGuDn1sZv5fGE2LJW4DSDpCuXWfcc-5LwKZR-HTZx8xVM_ZngB7DBVmYRZYbRcVnK5Ax8tFjBI3SP0OLGLVtDMC7scv9=w1097-h570-s-no-gm" alt=""/></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com